{
  "$schema": "https://json.schemastore.org/tsconfig",

  "_comment": [
    "TypeScript Strict Mode Migration Configuration",
    "",
    "This file defines the target strict mode settings for all Wundr packages.",
    "It mirrors config/typescript/tsconfig.base.json (which is already fully strict)",
    "and serves as documentation for the migration plan.",
    "",
    "Migration order (per package, one flag at a time):",
    "  1. strictBindCallApply     - rarely triggers errors",
    "  2. strictFunctionTypes     - catches contravariance bugs",
    "  3. noImplicitReturns       - forces explicit returns",
    "  4. noImplicitAny           - biggest batch, most valuable",
    "  5. strictNullChecks        - most impactful, null/undefined handling",
    "  6. strictPropertyInitialization - constructor/definite assignment",
    "",
    "Package migration waves:",
    "  Wave 1 (low risk):   packages/shared-config, packages/core, tsconfig.dev.json",
    "  Wave 2 (medium risk): @wundr/docs, packages/cli",
    "  Wave 3 (high risk):  @wundr/computer-setup",
    "",
    "Packages already strict:",
    "  @wundr/core, @wundr/config, @wundr/dashboard, @wundr/plugin-system,",
    "  @wundr/security, @wundr/environment (via base), packages/analysis-engine (via base),",
    "  packages/web-client (via base), tools/web-client, tests/",
    "",
    "See: .claude/analysis/wave2/22-cicd-pipeline.md for full details"
  ],

  "compilerOptions": {
    "target": "ES2020",
    "lib": ["ES2020"],
    "module": "CommonJS",
    "moduleResolution": "node",

    "declaration": true,
    "declarationMap": true,
    "sourceMap": true,
    "removeComments": false,
    "importHelpers": true,
    "downlevelIteration": true,

    "isolatedModules": true,
    "allowSyntheticDefaultImports": true,
    "esModuleInterop": true,
    "forceConsistentCasingInFileNames": true,

    "strict": true,
    "noImplicitAny": true,
    "strictNullChecks": true,
    "strictFunctionTypes": true,
    "strictBindCallApply": true,
    "strictPropertyInitialization": true,
    "noImplicitThis": true,
    "useUnknownInCatchVariables": true,
    "alwaysStrict": true,
    "noUnusedLocals": true,
    "noUnusedParameters": true,
    "exactOptionalPropertyTypes": false,
    "noImplicitReturns": true,
    "noFallthroughCasesInSwitch": true,
    "noUncheckedIndexedAccess": true,
    "noImplicitOverride": true,
    "noPropertyAccessFromIndexSignature": false,

    "skipLibCheck": true,
    "resolveJsonModule": true,
    "allowJs": true,
    "checkJs": false,

    "experimentalDecorators": true,
    "emitDecoratorMetadata": true
  }
}
